    "description": "Infrared Medium Resolution Scanner.\nThis camera is built under China responsibility and it is an upgrade of the Infrared Multispectral Scanner (IRMSS) of the CBERS-1 and 2 satellites.  \nIt has 4 spectral bands: \n\nB09: 0,50 - 0,90 ?m\n\nB10: 1,55 - 1,75 ?m\n\nB11: 2,08 - 2,35 ?m\n\nB12: 10,4 - 12,5 ?m\n\nIts spatial resolution  is 40 meters in the panchromatic and SWIR (shortwave infrared) bands and  80 meters in the thermal band.\n\nA complete coverage cycle of the panchromatic camera takes 26 days.",
